    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单易玩✕再次严酷冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/5a2fdb142831a817714ee9be0769bdcd.poster.avif?t=1739337058\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/5a2fdb142831a817714ee9be0769bdcd.webm?t=1739337058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/5a2fdb142831a817714ee9be0769bdcd.mp4?t=1739337058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buriedbornes2 是易于上手的回合制地牢 RPG 系列的续作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该系列广受欢迎，总用户数已突破 250 万，其进化形式使游戏更容易上手，更能让玩家自由享受游戏的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从两个选项中选择您想前进的房间，决定您想获得的物品，从最多 5 个技能中选择下一个技能，等等......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单、非实时的操作让您尽情享受严肃的冒险之旅，在这里，死亡是您唯一需要担心的事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Buriedbornes》系列最精彩的部分是创造了一个强大的角色，超越了可怕的不死大军并粉碎了他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >死亡之战与合作 &quot;联盟&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/d71751bf0995f01f4cd820b5ca07a5b5.poster.avif?t=1739337058\" width=600 height=265 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/d71751bf0995f01f4cd820b5ca07a5b5.webm?t=1739337058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于 &quot;远古霸主 &quot;及其尸体大军的入侵，世界正处于毁灭的边缘，这是最古老的预言所暗示的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将通过获取尸体、改造尸体以及使用 &quot;埋葬者 &quot;的禁术附身灵魂，反复挑战危险的地下城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场没有救赎和结局的无望之战，但人类尚未放弃一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界各地，幸存者群体怀着各自的目标继续抵抗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过互相帮助，我们或许能找到希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种族、职业、出身、装备、技能、符文......无数组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/9c47a8d2a7ae74253c21b3ea2f104076.poster.avif?t=1739337058\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581950/extras/9c47a8d2a7ae74253c21b3ea2f104076.webm?t=1739337058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险开始时，可以通过选择种族、职业和使用的尸体来源来创建角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个地牢中可以找到的每件传奇装备都有其独特的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可拥有 5 种技能，每种技能最多可设置 5 个技能符文，这些符文也可以在地下城中获得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些元素让您可以从无数选项中自由构建战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以有条不紊地构建自己的战术，也可以随机应变，通过意想不到的巧合发现强大的战术。</p>",
